      <h2>The Problem with Manual Commission Tracking</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/50 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-4">📊 The Cost of Manual Commission Tracking</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
