          <div class="rounded-lg bg-ink-800/50 p-3"><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-400">$6.5K</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Annual time cost for 5-artist studio</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-ink-800/50 p-3"><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-400">12%</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Average commission error rate (manual)</p></div>
